1.en: price rank in 9 hours, 1 if now lowest price, 9 if highest

2.en: price rank in 24 hours, 1 if now lowest price, 24 if highest

20.en: solar power forecast for next 24 hours, 0.. ca.25

21.en: value of future solar power, next 24 h, cents

22.en: average price of future solar power, next 24 h, c/kWh

23.en: amount future avarage solar power price is higher than current price, +- c/kWh

100.en: true if there is extra production, measured from grid or inverter production

101.en: average production  in current period, W

102.en: average power exported to the grid in current period, W

103.en: energy exported to the grid in current period, Wh

111.en: current month and day, e.g. 501 fir first of May

116.en: current hour and minute, e.g. 1200 - noon

130.en: true if day tariff (Finnish tariff, 0700-2200) effective

140.en: true if winter day tariff (Finnish) effective
